EXTRACTED VALUE: Was selected to the State Farm Holiday Classic all-tournament team in 1998, 1999 and 2000.
Holds the University of Memphis career record for 3-pointers made (287), which ranks in Conference USA history,
Was the first player in Mountain West Conference history to record multiple career games with 20+ points and 20+ rebounds.
4× NBA regular season leader for total assists: 2005 (861), 2006 (826), 2007 (884), 2010 (892)
In college, Jason always slept in his jersey the night before a game.
– West Coast Conference Player of the Week: November 26, 2007 and December 26, 2007
